title: 07/30/21 DPS Hour 3 Alyssa Naeher and Chris Mannix
itunes:title: 07/30/21 DPS Hour 3 Alyssa Naeher and Chris Mannix
description:
Chris Mannix talks to Dan about all the news from around the NBA. USWNT Goalie Alyssa Naeher talks to Dan about the importance of their Olympics quarterfinal win over the Netherlands. Alyssa says that there was a small celebration but that it didn't last long.
